        {
            "title": "馬查多將諾貝爾和平獎獎章贈予特朗普 挪威直呼「難以置信」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>周四在白宮會晤<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:委內瑞拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/委內瑞拉\">委內瑞拉</a>反對派領袖馬查多時，接受了她贈予的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:諾貝爾和平獎;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/諾貝爾和平獎\">諾貝爾和平獎</a>獎章。委內瑞拉的未來正在由美國主導塑造之際，馬查多試圖重獲特朗普的青睞。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數小時後，特朗普在社交媒體發文稱，會見馬查多是「莫大榮幸」，並稱讚她「歷經坎坷，是位了不起的女性」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「瑪麗亞將她的諾貝爾和平獎贈予我，以表彰我的工作，」特朗普表示，「這是相互尊重的美好姿態。謝謝你，瑪麗亞！」據白宮官員證實，特朗普接受了該獎章。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-127e5a83-9526-3f4c-a5d0-3d1c99cfe3ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"觀看：委內瑞拉反對派領袖瑪麗亞·科琳娜·馬查多談及在白宮會晤中將諾貝爾和平獎獎章贈予特朗普的決定。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gPUk7B_FLvboQ1C1jv0gEw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ec1336d34992eb5b5c0fce382c13463c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：委內瑞拉反對派領袖瑪麗亞·科琳娜·馬查多談及在白宮會晤中將諾貝爾和平獎獎章贈予特朗普的決定。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自1月3日美軍抓捕尼古拉斯·馬杜羅以來，馬查多始終被排除在委內瑞拉領導層更迭之外。她表示，向特朗普贈予獎章是為了表彰他對委內瑞拉人民自由所作出的貢獻。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她引述了19世紀初的一則歷史典故：拉法葉侯爵曾向解放南美洲大部分地區脫離西班牙統治的西蒙·玻利瓦爾贈送一枚印有喬治·華盛頓肖像的勛章。她稱此舉象徵著「美國人民與委內瑞拉人民之間的兄弟情誼」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">挪威對馬查多將獎章贈予特朗普的消息表示難以置信，特朗普長期以來一直渴望獲得該獎項。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">奧斯陸大學教授、前政界人士Janne Haaland Matlary向挪威廣播公司表示，「這完全聞所未聞。」她稱此舉「毫無意義」且「可悲」，並指出「此舉完全是對該獎項的蔑視」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">挪威諾貝爾委員會上周在聲明中表示，該獎項不可共享或轉讓。該委員會周五未回應尋求置評的電話和短訊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Trump Praises Venezuela’s Machado for Giving Him Her Nobel Medal</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Norway Stunned After Machado Gifts Nobel Prize Medal to Trump</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 John Harney、Derek Wallbank.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
